。動怒只會失去理智，令對手更易乘虛而入。無錯，已經越嚟越多浮屍，2019年仲有啲咁嘅野係好撚嬲。但比起嬲、比起只能喺國際間、fb上叫救命，遠水不能夠近火，如果能夠全民皆兵，自己香港自己救，相信到時港獨又好、雙普選又好、真一國兩制都好，香港人都可以擁有！<br />\n<br />\n打仗，要贏！梁天琦講嘅。（喺《地厚天高》入面講）"},{"pid":"dfeac571e78593be3d35034c7ee1b27d739b72aa","tid":1610691,"uid":276715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:12:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0155dc9c2010f96aadfa46dc85e3fbca9353a107","tid":1610691,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:13:43.000Z","msg":"無嘜特別，亦無必要理，<br />\n要對準暴政！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2398a54ff7f60f850dcefc5dc9db579bd5379f03","tid":1610691,"uid":162406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:20:31.000Z","msg":"好驚見到呀臣呀 好彩冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727d44ea28823581fefcad9d36405f7742b42fc3","tid":1610691,"uid":251872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:21:49.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n721 唔見人<br />\n831 打死人<br />\n101 射死人"},{"pid":"64c5a05653fce3c2d5123134020fbd92a1bbd9bb","tid":1610691,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:32:05.000Z","msg":"有啲藝人好難唔被迫表態既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正就算奶共對呢場運動影響唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bc206b6923b5dc0c8f195a3ebb461ed80221c1","tid":1610691,"uid":54223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:42:50.000Z","msg":"肉酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac